title: Tata Martino FIRES SHOTS at MLS and Hector Herrera! Will the Mexico midfielder be dropped? | ESPN FC

media:group.media:title: Tata Martino FIRES SHOTS at MLS and Hector Herrera! Will the Mexico midfielder be dropped? | ESPN FC
media:group.media:description:
ESPN FC’s Herculez Gomez joins Sebastian Salazar on Futbol Americas to discuss Tata Martino’s comments about Hector Herrera’s move to Houston Dynamo and whether he will still start for Mexico at the World Cup.
